Class HeidelTimeOpenNLP

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.uima.analysis_component.AnalysisComponent_ImplBase
      • org.apache.uima.analysis_component.Annotator_ImplBase
        • org.apache.uima.analysis_component.JCasAnnotator_ImplBase

            • uhh_lt.newsleak.annotator.HeidelTimeOpenNLP
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.uima.analysis_component.AnalysisComponent

    public class HeidelTimeOpenNLP
extends org.apache.uima.fit.component.JCasAnnotator_ImplBase
    HeidelTime finds temporal expressions and normalizes them according to the TIMEX3 TimeML annotation standard. This class is based on: https://github.com/HeidelTime/heideltime/blob/master/src/de/unihd/dbs/uima/ annotator/heideltime/HeidelTime.java We modified it to fit into the newsleak pipeline (accepting our type system and the absence of pos tags).
    Author:
    jannik stroetgen
